<div class="section-container">
    <div class="marketing-header">
        <h1>用户注册</h1>
    </div>
    <form class="form" method="post">
            <div class="input-unit">
                <label for="username">用户名</label>
                <input class="input" type="text" name="username" id="username">
            </div>
            <div class="input-unit">
                <label for="password">密码</label>
                <input class="input" type="password" name="password" id="password">
            </div>
            <div class="input-unit">
                <label for="password-repeat">重复密码</label>
                <input class="input" type="password" name="password-repeat" id="password-repeat">
            </div>
            <div class="input-unit">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-red">注册</button>
            </div>
            <div class="input-unit">
            <% if(success.length > 0){%>
                <div class="info-success"><%= success %></div>
            <% } %>
            <% if(error.length > 0){ %>
                <div class="info-error"><%= error %></div>
            <% } %>
            </div>
    </form>
    <div class="form-info">
        <p>请先看一下说明：</p>
        <p>－用户名不得大于十个字符，不得小于四个字符，可以使用汉字。</p>
        <p>－密码应大于八个字符，小于十八个字符，只能使用数字和字母。</p>
    </div>
    
</div>